Package stock.controller.commands

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CreateStrategyType
    An interface that represents a CreateStrategy type operation for various strategies.
    TradeCommand
    An interface that represents a command for this program.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCreateByStrategy
    An abstract class to help factor out common functions among various CreateStrategyType implementations.
    AddToPortfolio
    A class that implements adding stock to portfolio command.
    CostBasis
    A class that implements a command to get the cost basis of the portfolio.
    CreatePortfolio
    A class that implements a command to create a portfolio.
    CreateStrategy
    A command class to create a strategy in order to be saved for later use or applied immediately on a portfolio.
    CreateStrategyDollarCost
    A class that implements Dollar Cost strategy command.
    CreateStrategyRegular
    A class that implements command to add stocks in a regular way one by one.
    CurrentValue
    A class that implements a command to get the current value of a portfolio.
    DateHelper
    An helper class to get correct date from the user.
    Save
    A command to save a portfolio tp disk in text form such as JSON, XML, CSV etc.
